        <li>Long-term commitment for best price</li>
        <li>Interface can feel overwhelming initially</li>
        <li>Premium features require higher tier plans</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Who Should Use Which?</h2>
    <p><strong>Choose ExpressVPN</strong> if you want the best overall VPN experience with speed, simplicity, and reliability.</p>
    <p><strong>Choose NordVPN</strong> if you want better value with more features, more servers, and a lower price.</p>

